E-Waste Aggregator Platform – Complete Operational Flow 

1. Client Requirement Creation 

Client uploads asset/scrap Excel sheet 
↓ 
System/Admin cleans and standardizes data 
↓ 
Client reviews and approves: 

Asset quantities  

Categories  

Pickup locations  

Target/expected price 
↓ 
Requirement status marked as Finalized  

 

2. Vendor Invitation & Qualification 

Admin sends audit invitation to approved vendors 
↓ 
Vendors Accept / Reject participation 
↓ 
Interested vendors submit: 

PAN India/service capability 
↓ 
Admin verifies and approves vendors  

 

3. Physical Audit Process 

Approved vendors schedule physical audit with client 
↓ 
Vendor visits client site for: 

Quantity verification  

Condition checking  

Serial number verification  

Weight estimation  

Material grading 
↓ 
Vendor uploads audit report/photos 
↓ 
Client/Admin reviews audit report 
↓ 
Audit marked as Completed  

 

4. Sealed Bid Process 

Admin creates sealed bid event 
(only for audit-completed vendors) 
↓ 
Vendors submit confidential bids before deadline 
↓ 
System locks bids after closing time 
↓ 
Admin reviews submitted bids 
↓ 
Top vendors shortlisted 

 

5. Client Review & Open Auction 

Client reviews shortlisted bids 
↓ 
Optional open auction/live negotiation starts 
↓ 
Vendors revise pricing in real-time 
↓ 
Highest/Best vendor selected 
↓ 
Auction marked as Winner Finalized 

 

6. Purchase Order & Payment Security 

System generates: 

Purchase Order (PO)  

Work Order  

Agreement copy 
↓ 
Vendor submits:  

EMD/Security deposit (optional)  

Advance payment (if applicable) 
↓ 
Pickup schedule finalized  

 

7. Pickup & Material Handover 

Client generates gate pass/handover approval 
↓ 
Vendor arranges vehicle/logistics 
↓ 
Material pickup completed 
↓ 
Handover documents signed: 

Delivery challan  

Asset handover form  

Weight slip  

Material acknowledgement  

 

8. Final Reconciliation 

Final weight/quantity verified 
↓ 
Shortage or excess reconciliation 
↓ 
Final commercial value confirmed 
↓ 
Invoice generated 

 

9. Compliance & Documentation 

Vendor uploads compliance documents: 

E-Waste recycling certificate  

Data destruction certificate  

Form 6 / manifests  

E-way bill  

Disposal certificate 
↓ 
Client verifies documents  

 

10. Payment Closure & Completion 

Final payment released 
↓ 
Transaction closed 
↓ 
Client & vendor ratings/feedback collected 
↓ 
Project status marked as Completed 

 

Recommended User Roles 

Client 

Upload requirements  

Approve audits  

Review bids  

Approve winner  

Verify compliance  

Admin 

Manage vendors  

Clean data  

Control auction  

Verify documents  

Track operations  

Vendor 

Accept invitation  

Conduct audit  

Submit bids  

Pickup material  

Upload compliance documents  

 

